latestPosts.caption:
Hustling in factories at 19 to building The Indian Garage Co., this journey has been about patience, pure grit, and staying true to the vision.

Join me as I share my story - the challenges, the learnings, and what’s next.

We’re just getting started, and there’s so much more to build.

Let’s create something real, together. 💪✨

Celebrating the essence of our Constitution, the strength of democracy, and the pride of being vocal for local. 🇮🇳 Here’s to a nation that thrives on unity, diversity, and homegrown dreams. Happy Republic Day! 

#theindiangarage #tigc #vocalforlocal #theindiangarageco #happyrepublicday

The Founder said, ‘Hit 100K, and Goa’s on me.’ We didn’t stop there—campaigns crushed, shoots nailed, and milestones unlocked. From boardrooms to beach chairs, it’s been a year to remember. Buckle up for 2025—we’ve got a lot in store (literally). 

#TIGC2024 #YearWrapped #MoreInStore

2024 was all about you—the TIGC family . Your love and support have fueled our journey, and we’re excited to share that 2025 has a lot in store… quite literally! More stores, more styles, and more ways to celebrate fashion together. Here’s to an exciting year ahead! 

#TheIndianGarageCo #Grateful2024 #TIGC2025 #MoreInStore #MadeInIndia #TIGCFamily

We’re honoured to receive Myntra’s Tech Threads ‘Best Meteoric Growth Brand’ award, but this is just another step in the journey

To Myntra, thank you for recognizing our growth and for constantly inspiring us to push the boundaries of Indian fashion. This award wouldn’t have been possible without the opportunities you provide for brands like ours to thrive, innovate and leave a mark on Indian fashion.
To our incredible TIGC family, your passion and creativity have turned challenges into milestones. 

And to our customers, this is your win as much as ours. Your trust has made us one of the biggest 𝐃𝟐𝐂 𝐟𝐚𝐬𝐭 𝐟𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐛𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐬 in India, and it fuels us to dream even bigger🫶🏻

[Award, Myntra, recognition, fast fashion brand]

#awardwinning #recognition #fastfashionbrand #theindiangarageco

After 10 years of perseverance and growth, the wait is finally over! @theindiangarageco_ has won the prestigious “Meteoric Growth” title at the @myntra Tech Threads 2024, and we couldn’t be more thrilled. This win is more than just an award; it’s the realization of a dream deeply cherished by our founder, @ananttanted and the entire team.

To our incredible team, this is a celebration of your passion, relentless hard work, and unwavering commitment. Our journey has just begun, and this recognition fuels us to dream bigger and aim higher.

A heartfelt thank you to @myntra for believing in us from the very start. Our partnership has been pivotal, and we are immensely grateful for the platform and trust that have helped @theindiangarageco_ soar to new heights.

A special note of gratitude to @surya_14kumar —your support, humility, and belief in TIGC have been instrumental in our journey. You’re not just a partner; you’re family, and a true lucky charm for us. We are honored to walk this path with you.

Here’s to the passion, the dreams, and the journey ahead. This is only the beginning of TIGC’s meteoric rise! 🚀

latestPosts.caption:
Today marks a day of joy as I reflect on a 13-year journey filled with hard work, determination, grit and, most importantly, patience. This recognition is a testament to the belief that one day, all the grind does make sense.

From starting with a humble ₹10 lakh government loan to reaching this milestone, it’s been a path less travelled, challenging yet rewarding.

I’m deeply grateful to my mentor, Mr. Sanjay Dalmia, whose insights and support have been pivotal in my journey.

A massive shoutout to Business World, the esteemed jury of Aman Gupta, Annurag Batra, Sudhakar Rao, Nikhil B., Ashish Singla, Rohit Rajput, Jyoti Khetarpal, Tej Kapoor, Tariq Aboobaker for acknowledging our efforts at The Indian Garage Co. Awards like these aren’t just accolades; they’re powerful motivators that fuel our passion. 

Being recognised in this manner is both inspiring and heartwarming. It reinforces my commitment to the entrepreneurial spirit.

My door are always open to help all founders seeking guidance, advice, or a brainstorming partner. I encourage all aspiring entrepreneurs to feel free to reach out.

Here’s to building greater things together and making our mark in the business world!

#tigc #theindiangarageco #40under40 #businessworld #startup
